summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4136 for the improvement of 60th Avenue Southwest, from Admiral Way to Alki Avenue; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 49513, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
